<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/25025662">历史上有哪些为了自己目标特别能忍的人？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2192351" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">勾践的故事大家都知道我们不提。</div>


</div>
